description: Renovated East Side duplex condo with private direct-access from the street and garage that lives like a single family in South Boston. The main level features a large living room with a electric gas fireplace. A separated Modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite counters, a breakfast bar, open to the dining room. The second floor offers an office nook, in-unit washer/dryer, and two large bedrooms with en-suite full baths, expansive closets. Each floor has a large balcony. The basement level features an oversized mudroom that offers substantial storage space as well as a heated garage space and additional storage. Centrally located in the heart of South Boston, tucked away on a quiet street but only a couple blocks from the Super Market, Restaurants and bars such as Capo and Lincoln, and less than half a mile from the Beach. This home also highlights beautiful hardwood floors throughout, brand new HVAC system, and a professionally managed association.
